Download NodeJS - https://nodejs.org/en/
Install NodeJS
Download RubyInstaller - https://rubyinstaller.org/downloads/
Install Ruby
Install Jekyll - https://jekyllrb.com
Copy gulpfile.js - https://github.com/kdankov/jekyll-theme-lazy
Copy package.json
Run `npm install -g gulp-cli`
Create a folder `sites` in your user home folder
Create new Jekyll site
Copy files from labs
Rename your CSS files to SCSS files
Update .gitignore
Create repo in GitHub
Push to repo
  